Assignment 5: Lighting

Name: Zach Anders

Dependencies:
	golang
	git
	libglew-dev (Required by Go-GL)

Build Instructions:
	1. Make sure you have the dependencies installed:
			$ sudo apt-get install golang git libglew-dev

	2. Now you should be able to build the application:
			$ make
	3. If it was successful, you should see "BUILD COMPLETE" at the end of your output
	4. You should see a './hw5' binary in your current directory. You can
		either run it directly or with 'make run'

Running Instructions:
	1. Build and run ./hw5
	2. Controls:
			W : Move Forward
			S : Move Backward
			A : Strafe Left
			D : Strafe Right
			L : Toggle automatic rotating light
			Q : Move Light left
			E : Move light right

			Arrow keys : Rotate camera manually
			Escape : Exit the program

Time Spent:
	6 Hours
